title: 2nd Floor Condo Available Now, Updated Kitchen & Bath, Balcony, Pool
posting_body: ['Second Floor Condo Available', 'Now, Updated Kitchen & Bathroom, Balcony, Underground Heated Parking', 'Property Address', '3399 Kent St #205 | Shoreview, MN 55126', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'To apply, go to <URL>.', ' Each adult would apply and upload last two pay statements and proof of any other income.', 'Second floor condo available now in Shoreview.', ' Open floor plan between the living room, dining area and kitchen.', ' The kitchen has updated cabinets, granite counters and all appliances including a dishwasher and microwave.', ' The living room has a walkout to the large balcony which overlooks the back yard.', ' The bedroom is large with ample closet space.', ' Bathroom has been fully updated as well with tiled floor and shower.', 'There is one underground parking space included and plenty of additional parking in the lot outside.', 'This community has an outdoor pool, clubhouse with sauna, and access to a private beach on Lake Owasso.', 'SORRY NO PETS', 'Rent includes gas, water, trash & association dues', '$50 Application fee per Adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'for more information', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 760', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,150.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,150.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats not allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
